replies.body:
Read the message you replied to very carefully. He didn't advice to give infinite mana to mages (late or early game), he stated that whilst other classes can heal off from minions, or do enough DPS from AA's or those that use energy; mages on the other hand without mana are handicapped. 

In lane, nearly all the champions need mana management, except energy based champions, but mages also now have to worry about managing mana late game (no morellos passive), whereas other champions at this point, at the very least can farm/damage with minimal mana usage or with just AA, hence he said "their method of dealing damages is very limited."

Moral of the story: Give us more mana regen late game (when lost chapter is of no use), instead of us buying {{item:3027}} {{item:3040}}
